- Fitness goals include objectives such as weight loss or muscle gain, which can be inferred from the goal type and target value; 
- Progress details imply the latest measurement data, which includes various body circumference measurements; 
- Attendance and personal training sessions are tracked to monitor member engagement and progress towards their fitness goals.
